## Comparison

| | `KeyboardAvoidingView` | `react-native-keyboard-aware-scroll-view` | **FieldFlow** |
|---|---|---|---|
| Avoidance jitter | ❌ Common | ⚠️ Sometimes | ✅ None |
| Auto Next / Done | ❌ Manual | ❌ Manual | ✅ Automatic |
| Ref management | ❌ Manual | ❌ Manual | ✅ None |
| iOS + Android parity | ❌ Different behavior | ⚠️ Close | ✅ Identical |
| Works with Expo | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| New Architecture (Fabric) | ✅ | ⚠️ | ✅ |
| Zero native code | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |

